The recent Green phase made no implementation change — the integration test was already green. Reviewing names across the module: this is a mature codebase with well-chosen, intent-revealing names. `quotePremium`, `settleClaim`, `assertDamagesCovered`, `policyBasePremium`, `sumApplicableRates`, `tallyBy`, `sumOf`, `roundUpPremium`/`roundDownPayout` all clearly state their purpose. No renaming is warranted.

